Class Description
Controller
This class is meant to hold the main and communicate between the selected view and model

This class is used for garden ratings and using this in the view to draw out the garden

This class is meant to test the functions within the Plant class
Model
This class communicates with the controller to tell the view the current state of the Garden, the current plant and the triggering of garden

The class is meant to test functions within the Model class
Plant
This class is meant to handle the types of plants and handle plant sorting/filtering
